 {
     foreach (var t in transformers)
         input = t.Transform(input);
     return input;
 }
 ```

 **Impact: Eliminates one array allocation per call for the common 1- and 2-argument cases. `params ReadOnlySpan<T>` eliminates it for all arities.**

